---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About WestGroup Financial Planning - Fee-Only Fiduciary Advisors Since 2010"
  description="Learn about WestGroup Financial Planning's 25+ year history of providing fee-only fiduciary financial planning services to high-net-worth families in British Columbia. Meet our experienced team."
  canonical="https://westgroupfinancial.com/about/"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-20">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
      <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-yellow-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-10 w-96 h-96 bg-green-400/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: -2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight font-['Playfair_Display']">
          <span class="text-white">About</span><br>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400">WestGroup Financial</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          For over 25 years, we've been British Columbia's trusted fee-only fiduciary financial planning firm, 
          helping high-net-worth families build and preserve generational wealth.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/25 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
            Meet Our Team
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="border border-yellow-400 text-yellow-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-slate-900 transition-all duration-300">
            Our Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 font-['Playfair_Display']">
            <span class="text-white">Our</span>
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400"> Story</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-lg">
              Founded in 2010 in Surrey, British Columbia, WestGroup Financial Planning began with a simple mission: 
              to provide transparent, conflict-free financial advice that truly serves our clients' best interests.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              As one of British Columbia's pioneering fee-only fiduciary firms, we've grown from a small practice 
              into a respected wealth management company serving over 1,000 high-net-worth families across the province.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              What sets us apart isn't just our expertise—it's our unwavering commitment to the fiduciary standard. 
              Unlike commission-based advisors, we're legally bound to act in your best interest, always.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Today, we manage over $500 million in client assets and have saved our clients more than $12 million 
              in taxes through our advanced planning strategies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-['Playfair_Display']">By the Numbers</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400/10 to-green-400/10 rounded-lg border border-yellow-400/20">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">25+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-300">Years of Experience</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400/10 to-yellow-400/10 rounded-lg border border-green-400/20">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">1,000+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-300">Satisfied Families</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400/10 to-green-400/10 rounded-lg border border-yellow-400/20">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">$500M+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-300">Assets Under Management</div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-400/10 to-yellow-400/10 rounded-lg border border-green-400/20">
                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">$12M+</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-gray-300">Client Tax Savings</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400/5 to-green-400/5 rounded-lg border border-yellow-400/10">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Our Credentials</h4>
              <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-300">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Licensed Investment Industry Regulatory Organization of Canada (IIROC)
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  BBB Accredited Business with A+ Rating
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  $5 Million Professional Liability Insurance
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Family-Owned, Third-Generation Business
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-800/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 font-['Playfair_Display']">
          <span class="text-white">Our</span>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400"> Values</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          These core principles guide every decision we make and every relationship we build.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1: Fiduciary Standard -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-1">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">Fiduciary Standard</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We're legally and ethically bound to act in your best interest, always. No conflicts, no hidden agendas—just pure advocacy for your financial success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2: Transparency -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">Complete Transparency</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Fee-only means you know exactly what you're paying for. No hidden commissions, no product sales—just transparent, straightforward advice.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3: Excellence -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-3">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 font-['Playfair_Display']">Pursuit of Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            We continuously invest in education, technology, and processes to deliver the highest quality financial planning services available.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
