        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Our experienced team of financial professionals is dedicated to your success.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-1">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-400 to-green-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
