          </p>
          <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">
            <div>CFP®, CIM, FMA</div>
            <div>University of British Columbia, Sauder School of Business</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Member 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm border border-slate-700/50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center hover-lift fade-in stagger-2">
          <div class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-yellow-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-slate-900" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 font-['Playfair_Display']">Michael Thompson, CPA</h3>
          <p class="text-green-400 mb-4 font-medium">Tax Strategy Director</p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
